This building will feature the latest smart technology linking residents to the hottest attractions within the 11 Street District with Concierge services and building amenities.
 
Amenities will include , common-area featuring museum-quality art and installations, modern and high design residential lobby space, Club WEST LAS VEGAS STYLE pool bar & lounge, 5 star culinary food experience, Las Vegas inspired Food Hall featuring the most eclectic restaurants and bar.

Having the flexibility of ownership while having a solid real estate investment with one of the most recognized brand names.
